EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO TAXATION -- SURPLUS FUNDS TAX CREDIT ACT
***
1 This act would mandate that any surplus state tax revenue received in any fiscal year would
2 be refunded to the taxpayers of this state on a proportional basis in relation to the personal income
3 tax liability incurred by the taxpayers in that fiscal year.
4 This act would take effect on July 1, 2025.
